            <title>[LOG4J2-2893] Reconfigure doesn&apos;t work for XmlConfiguration Log4j1 compat</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LOG4J2-2893</link>
                <project id="12310790" key="LOG4J2">Log4j 2</project>
